SALESFORCE RELEASE NOTES
New Connect REST API Resources

Get to know the resources available with Financial Services Cloud.

Get the data of a retrieval summary definition by using the root record ID and the retrieval summary definition ID
Make a GET request to the /connect/retrieval-summary/runtime/retrievalSummaryDefinitionApiName/rootRecordId resource.
New response body: Retrieval Summary Result
Create an application form with details
Make a POST request to the /connect/industries/application-forms resource.
New request body: Create Application Form Details Input
New response body: Create Application Form
Retrieve an application form
Make a GET request to the /connect/industries/application-forms/applicationFormId resource.
New response body: Get Application Form
